effen Hung) |last=Hung |first=Steffen |accessdate=September 6, 2014}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\" | [[RPM (magazine)|CAN]]<br /><ref name=\"CAN\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bac-lac.gc.ca/eng/discover/films-videos-sound-recordings/rpm/Pages/list.aspx?OCRText=Village+People& |title=Canadian Charts |publisher=RPM magazine. |accessdate=January 6, 2016}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[GfK Entertainment Charts|GER]]<br /><ref name=\"German singles positions\">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.de |title=German Charts |publisher=Charts.de [[GfK Entertainment Charts|Media Control]] |language=German |accessdate=September 6, 2014}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br /><ref name=\"Irish singles positions\">{{cite web |url=http://www.irishcharts.ie/search/placement |title=Irish Charts |publisher=Irish Charts |accessdate=September 6, 2014 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hFf8iFDu?url=http://www.irishcharts.ie/search/placement |archivedate=June 3, 2009 }}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[Single Top 100|NED]]<br /><ref name=\"Dutch singles positions\">{{cite web |url=http://www.dutchcharts.nl/search.asp?search=village+people&cat=s |title=Dutch Chart |publisher=Dutch Top 100 |accessdate=September 6, 2014}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br /><ref name=\"New Zealand singles positions\">{{cite web |url=https://charts.nz/search.asp?search=village+people&cat=s |title=New Zealand Charts: Song \u2013 Village People |website=charts.nz |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=February 4, 2015}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[VG-lista|NOR]]<br /><ref name=\"Swedish singles positions\">{{cite web |url=http://norwegiancharts.com/search.asp?search=village+people&cat=s |title=Norwegian Chart |publisher=Norwegian-Charts |accessdate=September 6, 2014}}</ref>\n\n! style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\"|[[Sverigetopplista